title: House of the Dragon S1: Episode 6 Preview
description:
Join us for a spoiler-filled discussion of House of the Dragon, looking at episode 5 and looking forward to episode 6, with guest Dr. Kavita Mudan Finn - medievalist and early modernist.

Dr. Kavita Mudan Finn: https://kvmfinn.wordpress.com/
